column3:
Mercy's Virgin Mongolian Kinky Straight bundles give you the perfect balance of volume and texture. Made from 100% virgin human hair, each bundle is full, soft, and free from synthetic blends or processing.

The kinky straight texture mimics natural blow-dried hair, making it easy to blend seamlessly while still holding its thickness and body. These bundles can be silk pressed for a sleek look, curled for added movement, or worn in their natural state for a textured finish.

Due to the texture of this hair, we will strongly recommend buying a WEFT SEALANT.
